instructions from 
	https://www.c-sharpcorner.com/blogs/android-with-xamarin-debugging-over-wifi

open cmd in Admin Mode
cd C:\Program Files (x86)\Android\android-sdk\platform-tools"
adb tcpip 5555
adb connect <ipaddress:5555> , adb connect 192.168.100.3:5555
adb devices

check your android ip instructions here
 https://ccm.net/faq/33725-how-to-check-your-android-ip-address

